atest/assets/svg/1f604.svg\"></span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Sunday, November 30, 2025 2:30 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1444772761234051194", "author": "ThePlexus", "author_handle": "ogplexus", "user_id": "387354110548115459", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/387354110548115459/ddc68d5fbb439c8628e89e04c2a655ef.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, November 30, 2025 2:31 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-30 2:31 p.m.", "text": "The hill on the edge of the crater thank you very much", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>The hill on the edge of the crater thank you very much <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😆\"\n    title=\"laughing\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f606.svg\"> <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😆\"\n    title=\"laughing\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f606.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1444773289762361454", "author": "RichardP", "author_handle": "cave_master", "user_id": "848859709774495744", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Sunday, November 30, 2025 2:33 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-30 2:33 p.m.", "text": "the signal I show is on a 5dbi rubby ducky antenna ... I am sure the 8dbi higer up will see far more", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>the signal I show is on a 5dbi rubby ducky antenna ... I am sure the 8dbi higer up will see far more</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1444788034049675434", "author": "mowcius", "author_handle": "mowcius", "user_id": "222799443890536449", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/222799443890536449/cb67ead0dcf8375d5a198a3b1d573884.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, November 30, 2025 3:31 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-30 3:31 p.m.", "text": "To me these look quite different. Mine shows tiny blips every second at something like 869.46, 869.49, 869.53, 869.57 @ThePlexus , yours looks like a repeating pattern quite dissimmilar to mine although in the same approximate range, and @RichardP 's looks like an absolute nightmare, perfectly in the same range as UK Narrow (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>To me these look quite different.\n\nMine shows tiny blips every second at something like 869.46, 869.49, 869.53, 869.57\n\n<span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"ogplexus\">@ThePlexus</span>, yours looks like a repeating pattern quite dissimmilar to mine although in the same approximate range, and <span class=\"chatlog__markdown-mention\" title=\"cave_master\">@RichardP</span>&#39;s looks like an absolute nightmare, perfectly in the same range as UK Narrow</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Sunday, November 30, 2025 3:32 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1444790333752737953", "author": "mowcius", "author_handle": "mowcius", "user_id": "222799443890536449", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/222799443890536449/cb67ead0dcf8375d5a198a3b1d573884.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Sunday, November 30, 2025 3:40 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-11-30 3:40 p.m.", "text": "I'll take my SDR into the city next week and see what I pick up there. So far I've not experienced any issues with interference though, just being nothing like in LOS of other repeaters so pretty rubbish links in/out", "content_html": "<div class=\"ch